00:18:35,029 --> 00:18:38,124
<i>Mr. Helpmann was very close
to your poor father.</i>

222
00:18:38,232 --> 00:18:40,166
He was very close to me.

223
00:18:40,268 --> 00:18:42,167
Still is.

224
00:18:43,204 --> 00:18:46,197
