you get to Information Retrieval.

225
00:18:46,307 --> 00:18:49,573
-Thank you, sir.
-You'll like it there.

226
00:18:49,677 --> 00:18:51,805
<i>You're not listening
to me, Mother.</i>

227
00:18:55,217 --> 00:18:58,209
